snippet.textDisplay:
I see all the bandwagoners jumped ship from Golden State and joined Lebron's fanboys to create the largest bandwagon fanbase of all time.
James isnt a god. James isnt the GOAT, Michael Jordan still is and always will be. Have people quickly forgotten that they didn't even make the playoffs last season with James on the team? Not to mention that tonight they were kept under 100 points without 2 of Orlando's starters, and James got blocked twice. I sincerely hope the Clippers take them down.

The worship he gets is just laughable. I look forward to his inevitable downfall and the time when this sport is respectable again.
